<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[Mix together fillet beef, rice wine, light soy sauce, cornstarch, cold water with your finger and marinade for 20m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[stir fry fresh chilies with the meat in oil high heat until it begins to change colour, about 2m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add spring onions, garlic and carry on for 20s]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add red pepper, green pepper and keep on stirring briskly for 2m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[sprinkle light soy sauce, salt, sugar over and carry on stir frying for 2m]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
